snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War - Winter Assault Trailer
snippet.description: On September 23rd 2005 we launched Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War - Winter Assault. It's been 10 years since then so we thought we would post the trailer we found in our archives as an Anniversary special! Thanks everyone for the continued support!
